    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320000/extras/642f26b1907cd083b24a1e6903c82ab6.apng?t=1741608654\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320000/extras/642f26b1907cd083b24a1e6903c82ab6.poster.avif?t=1741608654\" class=\"bb_img\" width=666 height=162 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tailscape is a metroidvania game with a cute puppy as the main character. On a strange night, your adventure began to save your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can use the environment or special abilities to advance further. You may discover shortcuts or hidden puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tread or hit hard on enemies. You can get resources from them to make your adventure easier, but sometimes, the vast one can block your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are not alone in this dangerous town. You can save those in trouble or sometimes work together to unfold the story of humans and animals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We aim to add more stories and regions, resources, items, and combat in the future. We will do our best to make a good indie game. Thank you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
